com.impinj.octane

Class AutoStartConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.impinj.octane.AutoStartConfig

  • public class AutoStartConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    The ImpinjReader can be configured to start inventory automatically based on several inputs including General purpose input (GPI) and time. This class holds the configuration for the Auto start feature.
